<p>I haven&#8217;t seen any Tasks problems personally &#8211; that&#8217;s one of my favourite apps. Driver installation can be tricky, but I agree that HTC&#8217;s software for non-mobile operating systems is poor. There are also thousands of apps for backing up data on Google Play, and ClockworkMod Recovery (<a href="http://forum.xda-developers.com/wiki/ClockworkMod_Recovery" rel="nofollow ugc">http://forum.xda-developers.com/wiki/ClockworkMod_Recovery</a>) provides backup and restore facilities that bypass the need for Android to be present or working at all, though I think the best method is Android&#8217;s built-in backup facility (there&#8217;s a vaguely approachable tool for using it here: <a href="http://forum.xda-developers.com/showthread.php?t=1844032" rel="nofollow ugc">http://forum.xda-developers.com/showthread.php?t=1844032</a>).</p>
